<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
  <title>Your New Pet: {{petName}}!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .pet-info {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
    }
    .pet-name {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #667eea;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .pet-details {
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .detail-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #555;
    }
    .detail-value {
      color: #333;
    }
    .amount {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #28a745;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .contact-info {
      margin-top: 15px;
      padding-top: 15px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #667eea;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #5a6fd8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üéâ Congratulations!</h1>
      <p>You've successfully adopted your new pet!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="pet-info">
        <div class="pet-name">{{petName}}</div>
        <div class="pet-details">
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Species:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{species}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Purchase Price:</span>
            <span class="detail-value amount">${{amount}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Adoption Date:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{purchaseDate}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p>Thank you for choosing Pete's Pet Emporium! We're thrilled that <strong>{{petName}}</strong> has found a loving home with you.</p>
      
      <p>Your new {{species}} is sure to bring you years of joy and companionship. Don't forget to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Schedule a vet visit within the first week</li>
        <li>Update your pet's microchip information</li>
        <li>Start training and socialization early</li>
        <li>Stock up on supplies and toys</li>
      </ul>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="https://petstore.com/pets" class="btn">View All Pets</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>Pete's Pet Emporium</strong></p>
      <p>Where every pet finds their perfect home</p>
      
      <div class="contact-info">
        <p>Questions about your adoption?</p>
        <p>üìß Email: support@petstore.com</p>
        <p>üìû Phone: (555) 123-PETS</p>
        <p>üåê Website: <a href="https://petstore.com">petstore.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
